        <li>The Emperor&#39;s Prayer</li>
        <li>Judica Me</li>
    </ol>

    <hr />
    <h3 style="text-align:center">I: The Fede Imperialis</h3>

    <h3 style="text-align:center"><br />
    ~</h3>

    <p style="text-align:center">A Spiritu Dominatus,<br />
    <br />
    Domine, libra nos</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">From the lightning of the Tempest,<br />
    <br />
    Our Emperor deliver us<br />
    <br />
    From plauge, temptation, and war,</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">Our Emperor deliver us.<br />
    <br />
    From the scourge of the Kraken,<br />
    <br />
    Our Emperor deliver us.<br />
    <br />
    From the blasphemies of the falllen,<br />
    <br />
    Our Emperor deliver us.<br />
    <br />
    From the begetting of daemons,<br />
    <br />
    Our Emperor deliver us.<br />
    <br />
    From the curse of the mutant,<br />
    <br />
    Our Emperor deliver us.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center"><br />
    <br />
    A morte perpetua,<br />
    <br />
    Domine, libra nos<br />
    <br />
    That thou shouldst spare none,<br />
    <br />
    That Thou shouldst pardon none,<br />
    <br />
    That thou wouldst bring them only death.<br />
    <br />
    We beseech thee, destroy them.<br />
    <br />
    ~<br />
    &nbsp;</p>

    <hr />
    <h3 style="text-align:center"><br />
    &nbsp;</h3>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">II: Imperialer Lobgesang</h3>

    <p style="text-align:center"><br />
    ~<br />
    Love the God-Emperor,<br />
    <br />
    For He is the salvation of mankind.<br />
    <br />
    Obey His words,<br />
    <br />
    for He will lead you to the light of the future.<br />
    <br />
    Heed His wisdom,<br />
    <br />
    for He will protect you from evil.<br />
    <br />
    Whisper His prayers in devotion,<br />
    <br />
    for He will save your soul.<br />
    <br />
    Honour His Servants,<br />
    <br />
    for they speak in His voice.<br />
    <br />
    Tremble before His majesty,<br />
    <br />
    for we all walk in His immortal shadow.</p>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">~<br />
    &nbsp;</h3>

    <p style="text-align:center"><br />
    &nbsp;</p>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">III: Battle Prayer of the Order of our Martyred Lady</h3>

    <p style="text-align:center"><br />
    &nbsp;</p>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">~</h3>

    <p style="text-align:center">If Thou seest a flaw in me - smite me,</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">If Thou knowest a fault of mine - burn me</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">With flames of fury and righteousness.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">If Thou seest light in me -grace me,</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">If Thou hearest this plea of mine - bless me</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">With wrath of fury and righteousness.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center"><br />
    ~</p>

    <hr />
    <p style="text-align:center"><br />
    <br />
    For I breathe by Thy will,</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">For I live by Thy laws,</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">I carry Thy word, O God-Emperor</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">I bring solace to Thy servants,</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">and ruin to Thy foes,</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">A fate of fury and righteousness.</p>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">~</h3>

    <p style="text-align:center"><br />
    &nbsp;</p>

    <hr />
    <p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">IV: Prayer of Devotion<br />
    <br />
    &nbsp;</h3>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">~</h3>

    <p style="text-align:center">O&#39; God-Emperor who is strength, I devote this life to you.<br />
    <br />
    O&#39; God-Emperor who is grace, I devote this life to you.<br />
    <br />
    O&#39; God-Emperor who is mercy, I devote this life to you.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">O&#39; God-Emperor who is valour, I devote this life to you.<br />
    <br />
    O&#39; God-Emperor who is light, I devote this life to you.<br />
    &nbsp;</p>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">~</h3>

    <p style="text-align:center"><br />
    <br />
    &nbsp;</p>

    <hr />
    <p>&nbsp;</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">V: A Battle Prayer of the Ordos Hereticus<br />
    <br />
    <br />
    &nbsp;</h3>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">~</h3>

    <p style="text-align:center">O&#39; God-Emperor, be with me as I walk in the darkness.<br />
    <br />
    O&#39; God-Emperor, watch over me as I carry Your light.<br />
    <br />
    O&#39; God-Emperor, armour me as I battle the wicked.<br />
    <br />
    O&#39; God-Emperor, surround me and restore me so that I may serve You always,<br />
    <br />
    In life and in death.</p>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">~</h3>

    <p style="text-align:center"><br />
    <br />
    &nbsp;</p>

    <hr />
    <p>&nbsp;</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">VI: Battle Benediction<br />
    <br />
    &nbsp;</h3>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">~</h3>

    <p style="text-align:center">Through trials, may the God-Emperor make me resolute.<br />
    <br />
    Through suffering, may the God-Emperor make me strong.<br />
    <br />
    Through pain, may the God-Emperor make me worthy.<br />
    <br />
    Through death, may the God Emperor make me whole.</p>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">~</h3>

    <p style="text-align:center"><br />
    <br />
    &nbsp;</p>

    <hr />
    <p>&nbsp;</p>

    <p style="text-align:center"><br />
    &nbsp;</p>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">VII: The Ninth Battle Prayer of the Order of the Sacred Rose<br />
    <br />
    &nbsp;</h3>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">~</h3>

    <p style="text-align:center">Be the agent of my blade-arm.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">Be the power in my armor.<br />
    <br />
    Be the spirit that guides my bolts into the flesh of foes.<br />
    <br />
    Be the fire in my heart.<br />
    <br />
    Be the force that drives my blood.<br />
    <br />
    <br />
    God-Emperor of Man, You are all we truly have or need.<br />
    <br />
    Move me, move through me, all in service to Your divine, perfect will.<br />
    <br />
    By this may all our enemies be undone and your name be glorified above all.<br />
    &nbsp;</p>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">~</h3>

    <p style="text-align:center"><br />
    <br />
    &nbsp;</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>

    <hr />
    <p>&nbsp;</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">VIII: Drussian Prayer<br />
    <br />
    &nbsp;</h3>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">~<br />
    &nbsp;</h3>

    <p style="text-align:center">I shall fear no darkness,</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">for the light is within me.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">â€‹I shall flee from no enemy,&nbsp;</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">for there is no enemy more terrible than cowardice,</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">and I will overpower it.<br />
    &nbsp;</p>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">~</h3>

    <p>&nbsp;</p>

    <hr />
    <p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">IX: Prayer of Adulation to the Emperor<br />
    &nbsp;</h3>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">~<br />
    &nbsp;</h3>

    <p style="text-align:center">O Immortal Emperor; have mercy on us, miserable unworthies that we are.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">O Master of the Galaxy: protect your flock from the alien.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">O Keeper of Light: guide our darkened path with Your radiance.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">We are your warriors and we are thine servants.<br />
    &nbsp;</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">We stand free from blindness of heart, free from Hipocracy, vainglory, and deciets,</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">but captive to hatred, malice, and anger to the filth, the alien, and the heretic.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">By Thy agony and bloody sweat; by Thy Golden Throne and Thy Death,</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">â€‹by Thy destruction and reemergence as the God of Men,</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">â€‹keep and strenghten us we who fight for Thee.</p>

    <h3 style="text-align:center"><br />
    ~</h3>

    <p>&nbsp;</p>

    <hr />
    <p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">X: Libation to the Emperor<br />
    &nbsp;</h3>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">~</h3>

    <p style="text-align:center">The Emperor is our guiding light, a beacon of hope for humanity in the darkness.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">As we serve Him, he is our greatest servant.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">As we pray for Him, His thoughts are only of us.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">In the dark, when shadows are with us, The Emperor is with us,</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">in spirit, and in fact.<br />
    &nbsp;</p>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">~<br />
    &nbsp;</h3>

    <hr />
    <p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">XI: The Emperor&#39;s Prayer<br />
    &nbsp;</h3>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">~<br />
    &nbsp;</h3>

    <p style="text-align:center">Adore the Immortal Emperor for He is our protector.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">Admire the Immortal Emperor for His sacrifice to mankind.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">Exalt the Immortal Emperor for His strict guidance.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">Revere the Immortal Emperor for His undying guard.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">Venerate the Immortal Emperor for His holy wisdom.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">Honor the Immortal Emperor for His eternal strength.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">Glorify the Immortal Emperor for His all-seeing vision.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">Praise the Immortal Emperor for his unending rule.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">Hail the Immortal Emperor for He is our Lord and Master.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">Worship the Immortal Emperor for without Him we are nothing.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">~<br />
    &nbsp;</h3>

    <p>&nbsp;</p>

    <p>&nbsp;</p>

    <hr />
    <p>&nbsp;</p>

    <p>&nbsp;</p>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">XII: Judica Me<br />
    &nbsp;</h3>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">~<br />
    &nbsp;</h3>

    <p style="text-align:center">Judge me, O God-Emperor, and distinguish my cause from that which is not holy.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">Deliver me from the injustice and deceit of men.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">Send forth Thy light and thy truth:</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">let them lead me; let them bring me unto Thy holy hill, and into Thy temples.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">Then I will go unto the altar of the God-Emperor, unto Him my exceeding joy: yea</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">Upon the harp I will praise thee, O God-Emperor, my God.</p>

    <p style="text-align:center">Hope in The Emperor, for I shall yet praise Him, who is the health of my coutnenance and my God.<br />
    &nbsp;</p>

    <h3 style="text-align:center">~</h3>

